view.name: Police Incidents
view.description: The Santa Monica Police Department Incident information includes crime and incident reports.  The Incident information provided on the Open Data portal dates back to January 1, 2006 and is updated daily. The Police Department continues to provide an online crime mapping system that offers the ability to include data from other surrounding agencies and establish e-mail alerts to crimes in specific areas.
